# ─── Data & Models (too large — share via Google Drive) ───────────────
# Instructions:
#   1. Download CICIDS2017 from https://www.unb.ca/cic/datasets/ids-2017.html
#   2. Extract data/raw/CICIDS2017_ML-CVE/*.csv
#   3. Extract data/raw/Friday-WorkingHours.pcap (optional, for pipeline testing)
#   4. Put trained models (*.pkl, *.h5) into models/
#   5. Put processed data (*.csv, *.npy, *.json) into data/processed/
#   → Or download all from: [Google Drive link here]
